{
  "_readme": "Expected-output model for out/factor_salience.csv (step 4, AGGREGATE) — the core results table (RQ ii/iii). Percentages are of threads per tier and must be 0-100; tones are mean VADER compounds in [-1, 1] (empty when no scored sentence mentioned the factor).",
